title: Duke Martin Tibbs of Louisa, Ky.
title_page: Duke Martin Tibbs of Louisa, Ky.
maintext: DUKE MARTIN TIBBS, 50, of Louisa, Ky., died Thursday, July 26, 2018, in King’s Daughters Medical Center, Ashland, Ky. Duke was born July 18, 1968, in Bluefield, W.Va., to Brenda Tibbs, who survives. In addition to his mother, he is survived by his siblings, Lisa Tibbs, Tina Mitchell, Michael Kincaid and Crystal Kincaid. Duke was preceded in death by his sister, Cherry Kincaid. As were Duke’s wishes, he will be cremated and a memorial service will be held at a later date. Young Funeral Home, Louisa, Ky., is assisting his family.
